        Creates an empty workspace project with the name starting with the given projectNameBase. Created project is guaranteed to be new in EFS, but workspace may happen to already have project with such url (left uncleaned from previous runs). Such project silently gets deleted.
        Parameters:
        projectNameBase - project name template
        Returns:
        the newly created project, or null if the creation failed
